FBIS4-62424 "drsov094_s_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-094 Daily Report 14 May 1994 Georgia Hunger Strike Threatened If Abkhaz Agreement Signed Hunger Strike Threatened If Abkhaz Agreement Signed LD1405172294 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY in Russian 1529 GMT 14 May 94 LD1405172294 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY Russian BFN [Text] A large number of people, including refugees from Abkhazia, gathered in front of the Georgian parliament today. They wrote a statement that was later read at the evening sitting of parliament. The statement demands that the Georgian-Abkhaz agreement should not be signed and yesterday's decision by parliament should be complied with. In the case of the opposite happening, a hunger-strike would be staged outside the parliament building.
